messages.message: I have an example where I am trying to let the model read checkboxes about what stays in the house and what is removed in a deed. In build I get a very different answer then when I run the app in production. Is that expected? In build it is perfect, in app run it basically says it can't answer

Hi Timo
In which aihub env are you trying this ?
Also are you enabling Cross page table support in project settings here ? There was a bug where the settings were not carried over to app settings - not sure if that was deployed into aihub.uat
Yes I have it turned on, might make sense since that should also trigger the checkbox detection, right?

yes correct , this was fixed with 23.39 and backported a few days ago - but dont think it is repushed to aihub.uat- https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C05BJCNKZAM/p1696520393171339?thread_ts=1696154586.899979&cid=C05BJCNKZAM
